snippet.title: Life and Debt: A Real Life Simulator Content Update Trailer
snippet.description:
Life & Debt: A Real Life Simulator is a 2D pixel art life management simulator. Life & Debt focuses on the beginnings of new home ownership after moving out of your parents' house. You will have to maintain your finances and cashflow while having a really bad shopping addiction.

You can check it out on Steam here: http://store.steampowered.com/app/799840/Life_and_Debt_A_Real_Life_Simulator/

Or on Gamejolt here: http://gamejolt.com/games/lifeanddebt/322322

Join our mailing list: http://staticcitygames.com/mailinglist
